window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Pros to dating Lex Bailey:</p> <p>Sexiest man I've ever seen.</p> <p>Panty-melting British accent.</p> <p>Talented baker.</p> <p>Cons to dating Lex Bailey:</p> <p>Turned me down when I asked him out...in front of my entire family...at my brother's engagement party.</p> <p>Oh, and he has a secret. A big secret.</p> <p>So...no. I don't think I'll be giving him any second chances. But my foster dog? He has other ideas. This dog has issues...and Lex's cat has the cure.</p> <p>Unfortunately, I'm not exactly a forgive and forget kind of person. And even though both my dog and I appreciate the help, this time, I'm not going to let him get close enough to break my heart. This time, Lex Bailey is staying at arm's length.</p>"; 
